{"tid":754423,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"爆相爆片： N手軚掉頭　Corolla周身傷","createTime":"2018-07-24T11:43:13.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-25T09:28:12.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"d0462fb8ce1d495f79ec2d03a9327a75047f6ced","tid":754423,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T11:43:13.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180724/20458827\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180724%2F20458827&d=UIUFL9x5%2FU%2FE5XejIp7dP6WGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=392c60c9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180724%2F20458827&h=c569b7e2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180724/20458827</a><br />\n<br />\n爆相爆片：<br />\nN手軚掉頭　Corolla周身傷<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180724/large/a1402a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180724%2Flarge%2Fa1402a.gif&h=568f47e9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■Corolla司機扭咗N手軚，撞鐵欄又撞鐵柱。讀者鍾先生提供圖片<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n揸車要窄路掉頭，有時真係好考司機嘅功夫。好似上周五（20號）傍晚6點幾，有個司機揸住部白色豐田Corolla私家車，喺觀塘海濱道萬兆豐中心後巷，諗住窄路掉頭返大路，結果佢扭咗最少十分鐘軚先掉到頭，最慘係駛前撞鐵欄、退後撞鐵柱先甩到身，搞到部車花晒，真係陰功豬！<br />\n<br />\n鍾先生當時喺對面大廈停車場攞車，咁啱睇到呢幕，佢話初時見到部白色車「咦？點解咁得意打橫霸咗條後巷嘅？」於是拍咗片。鍾先生話呢條後巷係單程路，周不時有司機偷雞泊車。<br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180724/large/a1402b.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180724%2Flarge%2Fa1402b.gif&h=d800400a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n前撞欄後撞柱<br />\n<br />\n片段見到條後巷真係幾窄，仲有車泊埋上壆，剩低嘅路啱啱夠一架貨Van駛過。當時部白色Corolla前面泊咗架銀色七人車，架Corolla想喺度掉頭，個司機不斷扭軚、駛前又退後，數唔清佢究竟扭咗幾多手軚，舞來舞去都唔掂。後嚟個司機好似唔理咁多，照退後由得車尾撞鐵柱，仲駛前撞鐵欄，撞爆埋左邊車頭泵把；其間右邊車轆揩到柱，佢仲落車睇㖭，幾經辛苦終於掉到頭。<br />\n<br />\n最神奇嘅係個司機雖然退來退去，幾次差啲揩到架七人車，但最後都無撞到嘅，要傷都係傷自己部車箒，都算係咁嘞。鍾先生話覺得個司機係新手，平日見入咗去後巷嘅車，都係直駛退返出去海濱道，唔會掉頭。呢件事令佢諗起早前有部的士駛咗入山頂盧吉道，都係撞到花晒先出返嚟喎。<br />\n<br />\n今年大年初二清晨，有個的士司機駛咗入有「仙橋霧鎖」之稱、仲係行車禁區嘅山頂盧吉道，結果駛到每個彎位都卡住，多次撞欄仲爆埋胎，最後要拖車到場花3個鐘先將部的士救離險境，警方票控咗司機擅闖禁區。  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n爆相爆片<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n爆相爆片： 師傅教落：打死火燈車尾出"},{"pid":"89a923b2bbd378abff5c4e0aedabca802ffd3ea6","tid":754423,"uid":99700,"like":46,"dislike":0,"score":46,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T11:49:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/24/194938_b1c4338897ffee2e8734e033dbf556e9.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F24%2F194938_b1c4338897ffee2e8734e033dbf556e9.gif&h=2b2643e9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0fbd4331c745a7db669d37ec8023cf78d8958c0c","tid":754423,"uid":2346,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T11:53:53.000Z","msg":"算係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n冇撞到其他人d車<br />\n難忘經驗黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2db60039dcb106749ad7219a01440f6535ce14e1","tid":754423,"uid":47492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T12:07:11.000Z","msg":"無片<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bce8f39537889a1111794fcea9cced29fb79032b","tid":754423,"uid":22585,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T14:58:36.000Z","msg":"直接尾出，唔好掉頭啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88e1927e96ebd03ca6c3f9a0e3d03886a3a8ceea","tid":754423,"uid":86418,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"bce8f39537889a1111794fcea9cced29fb79032b","tid":754423,"uid":22585,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T14:58:36.000Z","msg":"直接尾出，唔好掉頭啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy